title: LIVE from the Summit on the National Assessment of Psychology (SNAP)
itunes:author: UW-Green Bay Psychology Department
itunes:summary: In this special, off-season episode, Dr. Ryan Martin interviews six psychologists at the Summit on the National Assessment of Psychology (SNAP), hosted by the University of Wisconsin-Green Bay (June 21-25, 2016).  Featuring Drs. Regan A.R. Gurung, Jane Halonen, Kristin Vespia, Jim Diaz-Granados, Aaron Richmond, and Jennifer Thompson.
